Package: reliefweb
Title: A package to make Reliefweb.int data easy for statistical analysis.
Version: 0.1
Authors.R: "Luis Capelo <capelo@un.org> [aut, cre]"
Description: reliefweb allows the user to create tailored queries to the
 Reliefweb API and download the resulting data into a data.frame, making its
 subsequent analysis easier. It cleans the data leaving only relevant fields
 and standardizes dates.
Depends: 
 R (>= 3.0.2),
 jsonlite,
 RCurl (>= 1.95-4.1),
 lubridate (>= 1.3.3)
License: GPL v3
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
